articles.title: North Korea launches ballistic missile before US Vice-President Kamala Harris visits South Korea - ABC News
articles.description: The move follows the arrival of the nuclear-powered American aircraft carrier USS Ronald Reagan in South Korea.
articles.content:
North Korea has fired a ballistic missile ahead of planned military drills by South Korean and US forces and a visit to the region by US Vice-President Kamala Harris.
